<h3>Social Cadence Rules</h3>
<p>Promote each blog post at least 3 times in the first 7 days. Then reshare once per month for 3 months.</p>
<p>Most teams promote a post once and forget it. That wastes 90% of its social reach potential.</p>
<p><a href="/blog/repurpose-blog-content-social-media/">Learn how to repurpose blog content for social media</a> to maximize every post.</p>
